Paper: hep-th/9212039

Date: 1992-12-05

Title: On Free Boson Representations of the Quantum Affine Algebra

$U_q(\widehat{\sl}_2)$Authors: Kazuhiro Kimura

Comments: 12pages

A boson representation of the quantum affine algebra $U_q(\widehat{\sl}_2)$is realized based on the Wakimoto construction. We discuss relations with theother boson representations.